parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The dashboard lights blink or remain lit
the door locks fail to work
the vehicle is unable to start
the radio and navigation system need to be reset
the alarm system goes off randomly
the remote fob fails to operate
and the electrical system cycles on and off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The battery goes dead without warning
the vehicle's gadgets and accessories fail to function
and the air conditioning system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the navigation system can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety risks if the driver becomes lost or disoriented.
symptoms: The DVD navigation system burns out the DVD disk
the GPS locator provides incorrect location information
and the navigation voice gives incorrect commands.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the electrical system can cause electrical failures, which can lead to safety risks and vehicle malfunction.
symptoms: Water is found in the fuse box
the headlights remain on continuously
the dashboard lights remain lit
and the vehicle is unable to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of power steering assist, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or increase the risk of fatigue while driving.
symptoms: Power steering fluid leaks
smoke or burning smell under the vehicle
power steering tilt/reach function stops working
difficulty steering the vehicle
fatigue while driving due to increased steering effort.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering tilt/reach mechanism can cause discomfort and fatigue while driving, leading to increased risk of accidents or fatalities, especially when multiple drivers of different sizes use the vehicle.
symptoms: Power steering tilt/reach function stops working
difficulty adjusting the steering column to a comfortable position
fatigue while driving due to uncomfortable steering position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbag may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly, leaving occupants vulnerable to harm.
symptoms: The airbag or SRS light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag deploys incorrectly or in an unexpected manner
the airbag system malfunctions or is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning airbag sensor can cause the airbag system to fail or deploy incorrectly, leading to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag or SRS light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag deploys incorrectly or in an unexpected manner
the airbag system malfunctions or is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate airbag deployment can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbag may not provide sufficient protection to occupants.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag deploys incorrectly or in an unexpected manner
the airbag system malfunctions or is faulty
occupants suffer injuries or fatalities in a crash.
